comments: Kanter (POR) establishes a legal picking position by firming up and absorbing the contact from Beasley (DEN).
Kanter (POR) takes the allowed two steps after the gather. Kanter maintains his legal pivot foot after the gather.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact with Beasley (DEN) during the driving shot attempt.
McCollum (POR) and Plumlee (DEN) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Plumlee (DEN) makes contact to Aminu's (POR) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Lyles (DEN) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Hood (POR).
Turner (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during Thomas' (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Aminu (POR) has a resting forearm to Hernangomez's (DEN) front, but does not fully extend it to dislodge him during the rebound.
Thomas (DEN) makes contact to Turner's (POR) arm that affects his SQBR.
Turner (POR) moves legally alongside of Thomas (DEN) absorbing the contact from Thomas during the drive.
LLS shows Turner (POR) legally contests Beasley's (DEN) shot at the rim as he absorbs the contact and cleanly blocks the shot attempt.
Hernangomez (DEN) makes marginal contact with Turner's (POR) arm that doesn't affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Hernangomez (DEN) slightly jumps A to B into Aminu (POR), but the contact is marginal during his shot attempt.
Thomas (DEN) establishes a legal picking position and does not deliver contact to Aminu (POR).
McCollum (POR) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Lyles (DEN).
After Craig (DEN) and Turner (POR) engage, Craig makes some contact that doesn't affect his ability to rebound or pass.
[Observable in enhanced video] Thomas (DEN) stands on the lane line without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
RLS shows Craig (DEN) jumps A to B into McCollum's (POR) backside and makes contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Turner (POR) rests his forearm on Lyles' (DEN) back making marginal contact as the two are attempting to retrieve the rebound.
Beasley (DEN) makes contact to the arm of Turner (POR) during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Hood (POR) makes marginal contact with Thomas (DEN) during the shot attempt near the rim.
